title: Romeo stir up curiosity with unique blurry teaser images for 'Without U' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Romeo stir up curiosity with unique blurry teaser images for 'Without U' By yckim124 11 minutes ago 886 21 0 0 Google+ Romeo released some unique teaser images for their 4th mini album ' Without U '.
The 7 members are captured in a blurry cut. The focus is not set on the members but on the different objects behind them giving somewhat of a reverse bokeh effect. This mysterious focus is stirring up much curiosity about the meaning behind the images.
